title: Blossom Du Jour - Midtown
typeOfFood: Vegan, American, Fast food, Juice bar, Delivery, Take-out, Catering, Kosher
description: This Blossom Du Jour outlet opened in 2012. Billed as "shrewd fast food," it's a fast food version of Blossom Restaurant. Offers wraps, burgers, salads, comfort food, raw pizza, raw burrito, soups, fresh juices, smoothies, and sweets.
